reviewText: This was a great movie. I will watch anything with Rob Schneider in it; He is hilarious. Don't listen to that one hater who gave this a single star, as he is obviously not a movie connoisseur.

This movie is a ripp off of kung fu panda the other people who review this movie is fan of norm McDonald who is in it it has lame animation don't listen to the other people do rent or buy ripped off movie
I would normally never watch this type of film, but it has Norm MacDonald in it, therefore I must.
Norm macdonald is hilarious. Thus the movie is hilarious. He really carried the show.
Only watched this because of Norm Macdonald--it was only good because of Norm Macdonald!
Thanks to the great Norm MacDonald, this ranks up there as one of the best films of all time. A work of art. Absolutely stunning.
